<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-09-08 11:25 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4334 &Cx1f; ttj-z
u v BC-HEARST-FEATURE-BUDGET     09-08 0735
