   EDWARDS. Feature on Tom Watson's caddie, Bruce Edwards, who's
been in Tom's service for 25 years. It's been a transition for
Edwards as well. Howard Richman. 18-20.
</P>
<P>
   CHIEFS. Who is Danny Pope? This punter came out of nowhere to
win the Chiefs' job over veteran Louie Aguiar. Adam Teicher. 18-20.
Photos
</P>
