<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-09-08 13:37 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4496 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u f BC-ONBUSINESS-COLUMN-ART     09-08 0935
