<P>
   TIMOR-RDP (Jakarta) _ Ledeall: Indonesia rules out an
international peacekeeping force; the U.N. decides to pull out of
East Timor. Rumors abound that President Habibie might be forced
out by the military. By Seth Mydans.
</P>
