Becker.
</P>
<P>
   CHINA-U.S. (Auckland, New Zealand) _ Secretary of State
Albright, here for the APEC meeting, meets with the Chinese foreign
minister on the WTO and other issues. By Jane Perlez.
</P>
<P>
   KOSOVO (Pristina) _ A look how Bernard Kouchner, the head of
U.N. mission here, is doing, as he departs for New York to report
to to the Security Council; more violence is reported in the
American sector of the troubled province. By Carlotta Gall.
