u w BC-Y2K19-COX     09-08 0488
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-Y2K19-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    SENATOR SEES PROGRESS IN PREPARING FOR Y2K BUG
 &HT;    Moving in (w) Washington and (f) financial categories.
 &HT;    By MARILYN GEEWAX
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
