   &UR; SPORTS (s) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   FBN-JETS-PARCELLS (Hempstead, N.Y.) _ All this babble about Tuna
Bowls and one-upmanship and poetic justice. That's somebody else's
game. Bill Parcells isn't playing. By Bob Duffy. 850 words.
</P>
