<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-09-08 19:45 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5042 &Cx1f; tad-z
r l BC-SMITH09-COX     09-08 1833
