<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-09-08 20:34 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5099 &Cx1f; ttj-z
u s BC-BKW-COMETS-ART-HNS &LR;      09-08 0818
