VIDEO REVIEW: ``YOU'RE INVITED TO MARY-KATE &AMP; ASHLEY'S FASHION
PARTY'' 
 FOR IMMEDIATE RELEASE 
 FROM THE FORT WORTH STAR-TELEGRAM
</HEADLINE>
  World rights. 
 By MIRANDA LANGLET, Elementary School Student Reporter 
 Copyright 1999 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
 (Distributed by New York Times Special Features) 
<TEXT>
<P>
   ``YOU'RE INVITED TO MARY-KATE &AMP; ASHLEY'S FASHION PARTY''
</P>
<P>
   Price: $12.95.
</P>
<P>
   Plot: The twins decide they want to learn about fashion design
and coincidentally, they meet some boys whose sister attends Los
Angeles' Fashion Institute of Design and Merchandising.
</P>
<P>
   The boys get their sister to take Mary-Kate and Ashley for a
tour of the college. Before they know it, the girls are in a major
fashion show that is broadcast on television.
</P>
<P>
