for instance when they laugh it is exaggerated and corny and goes
on too long. They sing a lot of songs but the songs aren't good
because they sing the same verses over and over and the beat is
just not interesting.
</P>
<P>
   There really wasn't a story line and I couldn't help but yawn.
</P>
