Mary Pierce of France during their match at the U.S. Open on
Wednesday. The American saved two match points and then came out
attacking after a 70-minute rain delay to beat Pierce, 6-2, 3-6,
7-5 to reach the semifinals. (Barton Silverman/New York Times
