<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-ADVISORY-LATINTRADE-NYTSF </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 
 This ``separate buy'' article is from Latin Trade magazine,
America's leading journal of Latin American business, finance and
trade: &HT;    ROCKET MAN: Q&AMP;A WITH STARMEDIA FOUNDER AND CEO FERNANDO
ESPUELAS. Latin America's Internet star, StarMedia's Fernando
Espuelas, talks about the difficulties of staying bright in an
expanding galaxy.
 &HT;    Filed as BC-STARMEDIA:ESPUELAS-INTVU-LATINTRADE-NYTSF.
