<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-09-08 22:30 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5247 &Cx1f; taf-z
u k BC-EDIT-OBSERVER-NYT &LR;      09-08 0631
